vice对Redis的读写操作延迟显著增加，HGET操作从1.7秒增至22.5秒，这可能影响了整个购物车相关功能。\n\n3. **级联影响**：Redis延迟导致CartService变慢，进而影响CheckoutService的PlaceOrder操作，形成级联故障。\n\n4. **异常分布**：故障涉及多个节点（aiops-k8s-03到08），表明问题具有系统性，而非单个节点故障。\n\n建议下一步深入分析Redis和AdService的资源使用情况，确认是否存在资源瓶颈或配置问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的故障时间段指标数据，我已经完成了全面扫描分析。以下是异常发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"memory_usage\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"内存使用率异常增加，memory_usage从正常中位数153MB上升到195MB，增长比例23.65%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"memory_usage: normal_median=153415680.0, fault_median=194564096.0, change_ratio=0.2365\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常飙升，pod_cpu_usage从0.01增加到0.6，增长比例193.44%，同时rrt和rrt_max显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: normal_median=0.01, fault_median=0.6, change_ratio=1.9344; rrt: normal_median=3073.25, fault_median=21377.46, change_ratio=1.4972; rrt_max: normal_median=42983.5, fault_median=197984.0, change_ratio=1.2865\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常增加，pod_cpu_usage从0.0增加到0.6，增长比例200%，同时rrt和rrt_max显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.6, change_ratio=2.0; rrt: normal_median=5915.33, fault_median=12636.25, change_ratio=0.7246; rrt_max: normal_median=42723.0, fault_median=94595.0, change_ratio=0.7555\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU使用率异常增加，pod_cpu_usage从0.0增加到0.6，增长比例200%，同时rrt和rrt_max显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=0.6, change_ratio=2.0; rrt: normal_median=5873.2, fault_median=13343.58, change_ratio=0.7775; rrt_max: normal_median=42682.0, fault_median=96255.0, change_ratio=0.7712\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"最大响应时间异常增加，rrt_max从14655.5增加到16500.0，同时p99值从92023.52飙升到918971.52，增长比例